# Consultingsmiths

## That guy named Smith who used to be a consultant

### Welcome to the new site

There was once a Wordpress site here—but it’s time to back away from all those big outfits and get back to the Internet that we got excited about in the ‘80s, and the Web that belonged to all of us before Google, Twitter, Facebook and the other walled gardens took over. You can’t get a Constultingsmiths app—you have to visit us with a browser, graphic or textual.

Have a good ‘un, my friend!
